name: growing pains
description:
This animated, glitch art inspired piece entitled "growing pains" explores human's interaction with nature -- and represents the Ace of Wands. As a supplement to my Tarot series, found on my store "When Tigers Smoked" at opensea, I am so excited to mint my first piece on HEN! 

As a trans woman of color artist and illustrator, this 7/7 piece uses rich colors, line work, and light to depict a moment of magic, understanding, and inspiration. 

Enjoy :)
